quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  49,1,"Ko onon yo …ìen gom…óim…ìe ! wata on adito yeeso Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko on. Hulee Allah. Pellet, Allah ko Nanoowo, Yi'oowo"
  49,2,"Ko onon yo …ìen gom…óim…ìe ! wata on towu sowtooji mon e hoore sowto Annabaajo on, wata on ewnor mo kadi konngol, wano no yoga mon ewnorta yoga, sakko golle mon …óen bonata, hara on so'aa-anndude"
  49,3,"Pellet, …ìen joltinoo…ìe sowtooji ma…ì…ìe …óin ka Nulaa…óo Allah on, ko …ìen woni …ìe Alla jarabii …ìer…óe mun …óen gom…óal. Hino woodani …ìe haforanal e njo…ìdi mawndi"
  49,4,"Pellet, …ìen …ìe no noddire ka …ìaawo cuu…ói, ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e ma…ì…ìe, wanaa haqqiloo…ìe"
  49,5,"Sinno …ìe mu√±√±ino haa yaltaa e ma…ì…ìe, ko …óum …ìuraynoo mo∆¥∆¥annde …ìe. Allah ko Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo"
  49,6,"Ko onon yo …ìen gom…óim…ìe ! Si faasiqiijo ardanii on e kumpital, tefee fii wata on he…ìor e yim…ìe sabu majjeede, wonton ninsu…ìe e kon ko wa…óu…óon"
  49,7,"Anndee wonnde Nulaa…óo Allah on hino hakkunde mon. Si o tewtino on e ko …óuu…ói e fiyakuuji, on tampayno. Kono Allah yi…óini on gom…óinal, O cu…óini ngal e …ìer…óe mon; O a√±ini on keeferaaku, e faasiqaaku e geddi. Ko …ìen woni feewu…ìe …ìen"
  49,8,"…óum ko …ìural immorde ka Allah e neema. Allah ko Anndu…óo, √ëee√±u…óo"
  49,9,"Si feddeeji …ói…ói e gom…óim…ìe …ìen ha…ìii, mo∆¥∆¥intinee hakkunde ma…ì…ìe. Si fedde goo bewii e hoore ndeya, ko ha…ìugol wonnde e bewude nden, haa nde ruttoo e yamiroore Allah nden. Si nde ruttike, mo∆¥∆¥intiniree hakkunde ma…ì…ìe nun…óal. Nun…óee, tawde pellet, Allah no yi…ói nun…óoo…ìe …ìen"
  49,10,"Anndee gom…óim…ìe …ìen ko jeydu…ìe. Haray mo∆¥∆¥inee hakkunde jeydal mon ngal, hulon Allah, belajo'o on yurminte"